The paper proposes a novel methodology for few-shot learning using deep neural networks, which is a topic that falls under the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE), and natural language processing (cs.CL). However, since the paper focuses on the development of a lightweight model for edge devices, it is most likely to be categorized under cs.LG and cs.CV, which are the sub-categories that deal with the development of efficient and scalable machine learning models.
